'''螺内酯'''（{{lang-en|spironolactone}}），[[商品名|商品名]]有'''安体舒通'''、'''Aldactone'''等，是一种常用于治疗[[心衰|心衰]]、[[肝硬化|肝硬化]]、[[胃病|胃病]]等引发的[[积液|积液]]的[[利尿药|利尿药]]<ref name="AHFS2015">{{cite web |title = Spironolactone |url = http://www.drugs.com/monograph/spironolactone.html |publisher = The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists |access-date = 2015-10-24 |archive-date = 2015-11-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151116054857/http://www.drugs.com/monograph/spironolactone.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此药也用于治疗[[高血压|高血压]]、补充后仍无改善的[[低血钾|低血钾]]，以及女性[[多毛症|多毛症]]；此外还用作[[跨性别|跨性别]]女性[[性别肯定激素治疗|性别肯定激素治疗]]（GAHT）中的抗雄药物<ref>{{cite book |last = Maizes |first = Victoria |title = Integrative Women's Health |year = 2015  |isbn = 9780190214807 |page = 746 |edition = 2nd |url = https://books.google.ca/books?id=uveJCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA746 |access-date = 2016-06-05 |archive-date = 2016-03-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305050257/https://books.google.ca/books?id=uveJCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA746 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。此药经口服用<ref name="AHFS2015" />。

<!-- 副作用和工作原理 -->
螺内酯的常見[[副作用|副作用]]包括[[電解質異常|電解質異常]]（尤其是[[高血鉀症|高血鉀症]]、噁心、嘔吐、頭痛、皮疹），以及性慾減退。<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->有肝腎問題的人服用螺內酯應當格外小心。<ref name="AHFS2015" />螺內酯在孕期的應用沒有經過足夠的研究，故不應用於治療{{link-en|孕婦高血壓|high blood pressure of pregnancy}}。<ref>{{cite web|title=Spironolactone Pregnancy and Breastfeeding Warnings|url=http://www.drugs.com/pregnancy/spironolactone.html|access-date=29 November 2015|archive-date=2015-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151202081203/http://www.drugs.com/pregnancy/spironolactone.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>螺內酯是[[醛固酮|醛固酮]]及[[睾酮|睾酮]]這兩種[[激素|激素]]的一種[[類固醇|類固醇]][[受體拮抗劑|受體拮抗劑]]，同時有某種類[[孕酮|孕酮]]樣效應。<!-- <ref name="AHFS2015" /> -->螺內酯是一種{{link-en|保鉀利尿藥|potassium-sparing diuretic}}。<ref name="AHFS2015" />

<!-- History, society and culture -->
螺内酯于1959年投入使用<ref name="Wermuth2008">{{cite book | author = Camille Georges Wermuth | title = The Practice of Medicinal Chemistry | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=Qmt1_DQkCpEC&pg=PA34 | access-date = 27 May 2012 | date = 24 July 2008 | publisher = Academic Press | isbn = 978-0-12-374194-3 | page = 34 | archive-date = 2021-04-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210414083232/https://books.google.com/books?id=Qmt1_DQkCpEC&pg=PA34 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Sittig1988">{{cite book | author = Marshall Sittig | title = Pharmaceutical Manufacturing Encyclopedia | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=XCsJgUnclbcC&pg=PA1385 | access-date = 27 May 2012 | year = 1988 | publisher = William Andrew | isbn = 978-0-8155-1144-1 | page = 1385 | archive-date = 2020-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201222094147/https://books.google.com/books?id=XCsJgUnclbcC&pg=PA1385 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。“螺内酯”被列于[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]，是基本[[卫生系统|卫生系统]]中最重要的药品之一<ref name="WHO19th">{{cite web |title = WHO Model List of Essential Medicines (19th List) |url = http://www.who.int/medicines/publications/essentialmedicines/EML_2015_FINAL_amended_NOV2015.pdf?ua=1 |publisher = World Health Organization |access-date=8 December 2016 |date=April 2015 |archive-date=2016-12-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161213052708/http://www.who.int/medicines/publications/essentialmedicines/EML_2015_FINAL_amended_NOV2015.pdf?ua=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；此药还是一种[[通用名药物|通用名药物]]<ref name="AHFS2015" />。在[[发展中国家|发展中国家]]，此药于2014年的批发价处于每日用量0.02到0.12美元的区间<ref>{{cite web |title = Spironolactone |url = http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=SPI25T&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=25%20mg&desc=Spironolactone&pack=new&frm=TAB-CAP&rte=PO&class_code2=16%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2816%2E%29Diuretics%3Cbr%3E|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide |access-date = 29 November 2015 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=no }}</ref>。而在美国每日则约需要0.5美元<ref name="AHFS2015" />。

